item.title: Shooting Untethered
item.description:
Shooting Untethered

Shooting Untethered Today I got to shoot artist and brother Jon Morris ( @jdmfinearts). It was a fun shoot, and we tried some different lighting setups. The images were shot in jpeg format and transferred to my cell phone via eyefi mobi card.

item.title: Parental Guidance These are my parents....
item.description:
Parental Guidance These are my parents....

Parental Guidance These are my parents. They don't stream movies, they don't understand wifi encrypted passwords, hashtags, or twitter feeds. My mom still has her Juno mail account. They don't use or understand what a Facebook is. I don't think that they have ever had an actual portrait taken off them.
